      "role": "user",
      "content": "they're just so tired of it though. i see it in their eyes when they come over. it's like every little thing i need is another chore on their list. i've spent my whole life looking after everyone else and now i'm just... i'm just making everything harder for them. it feels like there's no way to win.",
